The paper deals with algorithms for maximum matching on trees and special classes of graphs, which are topics in data structures (cs.DS), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), and graph theory (cs.GT). The paper also presents randomized and deterministic algorithms, which are topics in algorithms (cs.AL) and computational complexity (cs.CC).
